================================================================================
OpenCV frontal-face Haar cascade
================================================================================

The bundled file

    src/main/resources/cascades/haarcascade_frontalface_default.xml

is taken unmodified from the OpenCV project (https://opencv.org), at the
`haarcascade_frontalface_default.xml` path, and is included here to provide a
working default detector so users do not need to download it separately.

